    {
      "instruction": "<p>Meanwhile, combine <strong>half </strong>your<strong> soy sauce</strong> (you'll use the rest later!) and 40ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[60ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80ml]</span> <strong>very cold water </strong>in a small bowl – this is your <strong>soy stock</strong></p><p>Add 40g<span class=\"text-purple\"> [60g]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[80g]</span> <strong>flour </strong>and 3/4 of your <strong>cornflour</strong> to a separate large bowl with <strong>half </strong>your <strong>rice wine vinegar </strong>(you'll use the rest later!) and the<strong> soy stock</strong></p><p>Stir it all together until fully combined with no lumps, then set aside – this is your <strong>batter</strong></p>",
