      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Chinese takeaway-style chicken balls </strong>with the <strong>vegetable fried rice</strong> and <strong>sweet & sour sauce</strong> to the side</p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
